            <div id="content">
              <div class="page_heading">Agile Development</div>
<div class="about_us_detail">
  <p>We follow a systematic and time bound approach to web application development, adhering to the following key agile principles:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Short terms goals and smaller release cycles</li>
    <li>Product is built inside-out, i.e. starting from simple features and gradually adding more sophistication</li>
    <li>Stable version of product deployed frequently</li>
    <li>Test driven development to ensure high quality/reliability of codes</li>
    <li>Concurrent quality assurance to ensure bug-free product all the time</li>
  </ul>
  <br/>
  <strong>A typical software development cycle by RailsTeam:</strong>
  <img src="/assets/7/development-process.jpg"  alt='development-process' />
</div>
              
